<h2>
China
</h2>
<h3>
The most populous country on Earth and the growing economic giant of East Asia, China's return to prominence on the world stage has been hard to ignore. A traveler to China will get a glimpse of a society that is rapidly changing in many ways, and massively diverse in its customs, dialects, architecture, and food.
</h3>
<h4>Pros and Cons of Travel</h4>
